data.description: This spacious home is designed to accommodate your needs with 3 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. However, there is an additional room that can be used as a fourth bedroom or as a multipurpose space, depending on your preference.   Convenience is the key with this property as it is located just minutes away from the airport, making travel hassle free. This is especially useful for frequent flyers.  To fulfill your storage needs, the property offers two storage sheds. These sheds provide ample space to store your belongings, whether it be seasonal items, outdoor equipment, or any items that you prefer to keep tucked away neatly.  Parking will never be an issue, as it comes equipped with 5 car storage space. This feature is great or households with multiple vehicles or those who require additional parking for guests.  This home qualifies for 100% financing Rural Dev.
